      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Clad in Hellfire",
        "Client": "Armored Hunter",
        "Description": "What an embarrassment. My best\r\narmor was about as effective as wet\r\npaper against Magnamalo. I tell ya,\r\nthat hellfire is a one-way ticket back\r\nto camp... I guess I need to hit up\r\nthe Smithy again. Think you can\r\nfinish up the quest for me?",
        "Target": "Hunt Magnamalo",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Armure infernale",
        "Client": "Chasseur en armure",
        "Description": "Franchement, j\u0027ai honte... M\u00EAme ma\r\nmeilleure armure a pas fait long\r\nfeu face au Magnamalo et \u00E0 son\r\nsatan\u00E9 Feu de l\u0027enfer ! Bon, va\r\nfalloir que je retourne voir le\r\nforgeron. Dis, tu pourrais finir\r\ncette qu\u00EAte pour moi ?",
        "Target": "Chasser le Magnamalo",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Puro fuoco infernale",
        "Client": "Cacciatore corazzato",
        "Description": "Che imbarazzo! La mia migliore\r\narmatura era come carta\r\nstraccia contro il Magnamalo.\r\nQuel fuoco infernale spedisce\r\ndritti all\u0027accampamento. Forse\r\ndovrei ritornare alla Forgia.\r\nFiniresti la missione per me?",
        "Target": "Caccia il Magnamalo",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Ein Kleid aus H\u00F6llenfeuer",
        "Client": "Gepanzerter J\u00E4ger",
        "Description": "Wie peinlich. Meine beste R\u00FCstung\r\nwar gegen Magnamalo etwa so wirk-\r\nsam wie nasses Papier. Ich sag\u0027s dir,\r\ndieses H\u00F6llenfeuer schickt dich direkt\r\nzur\u00FCck zum Lager... Ich muss wohl\r\nmal wieder zur Schmiede. W\u00FCrdest\r\ndu die Quest f\u00FCr mich abschlie\u00DFen?",
        "Target": "Erjage Magnamalo.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Ataviado de fuego infernal",
        "Client": "Cazador armado",
        "Description": "Qu\u00E9 verg\u00FCenza. Mi mejor\r\nequipamiento fue in\u00FAtil contra\r\nlos ataques de Magnamalo,\r\nespecialmente ese maldito\r\nfuego infernal que usa.\r\n\u00A1Me rindo! \u00A1Que se ocupe\r\nun cazador mejor!",
        "Target": "Caza a Magnamalo",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u041E\u0431\u044A\u044F\u0442\u044C\u044F \u0430\u0434\u0441\u043A\u043E\u0433\u043E \u043F\u043B\u0430\u043C\u0435\u043D\u0438",
        "Client": "\u041E\u0445\u043E\u0442\u043D\u0438\u043A \u0432 \u0431\u0440\u043E\u043D\u0435",
        "Description": "\u0412\u043E\u0442 \u0442\u0430\u043A \u0434\u0435\u043B\u0430. \u041C\u043E\u044F \u043B\u0443\u0447\u0448\u0430\u044F \u0431\u0440\u043E\u043D\u044F\r\n\u043F\u0440\u043E\u0442\u0438\u0432 \u041C\u0430\u0433\u043D\u0430\u043C\u0430\u043B\u043E \u2014 \u0447\u0442\u043E \u043C\u043E\u043A\u0440\u0430\u044F\r\n\u0431\u0443\u043C\u0430\u0433\u0430. \u0421 \u0410\u0434\u0441\u043A\u0438\u043C \u043F\u043B\u0430\u043C\u0435\u043D\u0435\u043C\r\n\u043D\u0435 \u043E\u0447\u0435\u043D\u044C-\u0442\u043E \u043F\u043E\u0441\u043F\u043E\u0440\u0438\u0448\u044C. \u0427\u0442\u043E \u0436\u0435,\r\n\u043F\u043E\u0439\u0434\u0443 \u0441\u043D\u043E\u0432\u0430 \u0432 \u043A\u0443\u0437\u043D\u0438\u0446\u0443. \u0421\u043C\u043E\u0436\u0435\u0448\u044C\r\n\u0437\u0430\u043A\u043E\u043D\u0447\u0438\u0442\u044C \u044D\u0442\u043E \u0437\u0430\u0434\u0430\u043D\u0438\u0435 \u0437\u0430 \u043C\u0435\u043D\u044F?",
        "Target": "\u0412\u044B\u0441\u043B\u0435\u0434\u0438\u0442\u044C \u041C\u0430\u0433\u043D\u0430\u043C\u0430\u043B\u043E",
        "Fail": "\u0421\u0447\u0435\u0442\u0447\u0438\u043A \u043D\u0430\u0433\u0440\u0430\u0434\u044B \u0434\u043E\u0445\u043E\u0434\u0438\u0442 \u0434\u043E 0\r\n\u0438\u043B\u0438 \u0438\u0441\u0442\u0435\u043A\u0430\u0435\u0442 \u0432\u0440\u0435\u043C\u044F"
